    GET - nie zawiera Body, tylko parametry, nawet 20
GET /projects -> find all [page, size, sort]
GET /projects/{pid} -> find by id [404 when not found]
GET /projects + {parameters=criteria} -> find by criteria [+ np. dateRange like "lastMonth", "nextWeek"]
GET /projects/{pid}/boms -> findAllBomsForProject [page, size, sort]
GET /projects/{pid}/boms/{bid} -> browse single bom
.GET /materials -> get all materials [page, size, sort]
.GET /materials/{mid} -> find by id
GET /materials + {parameters=criteria}
GET /materials/{mid}/deliveries -> find all deliveries for given mid
GET /deliveries -> find all deliveries [page, size, sort]
GET /deliveries/{did} -> find one delivery
GET /projects/{pid}/check -> check if all necessary materials are in stock

    POST - zawiera Body (kompletne, bez id)
POST /projects -> create project
POST /projects/{pid}/boms -> create bom
POST /projects/{pid}/boms/bulk -> create list of boms
POST /deliveries -> create delivery
POST /deliveries/bulk
.POST /materials -> create material
.POST /materials/bulk
POST /deliveries/delivered -> set status to delivered for a list of deliveries

    PUT - zawiera Body (kompletne, bez id)
PUT /projects/{pid} -> replace project (?)
PUT /projects/{pid}/boms -> replace all boms for project (accepts List<Bom> in body)
PUT /projects/{pid}/boms/{bid} -> replace single bom
PUT /deliveries/{did} -> replace delivery
.PUT /materials/{mid} -> replace material

    PATCH - zawiera Body niekompletne, tylko to co siÄ™ zmienia
PATCH /projects/{pid} -> update project
PATCH /projects/{pid}/boms -> update bom (batch, List<Bom>)
PATCH /projects/{pid}/boms/{bid} -> update single bom
PATCH /deliveries/{did} -> update delivery
PATCH /deliveries/{did} -> special case: json = {"status":"Delivered"} -> set status of single delivery to Delivered, other fields are ignored.
.PATCH /materials/{mid} -> update material
PATCH /projects/{pid}/start -> update start date, adjust material stock
PATCH /projects/{pid}/stop -> update end date, adjust material stock

    DELETE - parametry (PathVariable, RequestParameter)
DELETE /projects/{pid} -> delete project
DELETE /projects/{pid}/boms -> delete all boms in project
DELETE /projects/{pid}/boms/{bid} -> delete single bom from project
DELETE /deliveries/{did} -> delete delivery
.DELETE /materials/{mid} -> delete material.

POST /auth/login
POST /auth/logout
